text: Phuket is an island province off the south-west coast of Thailand. Phuket may also refer to: *Phuket (city), the capital of the province, in the southeast of the island *Amphoe Mueang Phuket, the district covering the south of the island around the capital *Phuket (film), a 2009 Thai short film
title: Phuket (disambiguation)
